BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout at the Pence Gallery
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T210000
UID:c230d30c7b2dd59f304675f5c1a9de46@davischamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Community Event\n\nJoin us at the Pence Gallery for our 2nd Fr
 iday ArtAbout reception on April 10\, 6-9 PM. Enjoy browsing multiple art 
 exhibits\, a complimentary wine tasting by Fjord Oak Winery\, an art-theme
 d scavenger hunt\, and live folk music by Plain Folk in the courtyard (6-8
  PM). Free admission!\n\nThe Abstract Language of Ceramics | Apr. 10 - Jun
 . 3\n\nThis exhibit features the work of ceramic artists Karyn Gabriel\, M
 ark Goudy\, Kris Marubayashi\, Liza Riddle\, and Laura Van Duren. Together
 \, these artists create striking geometric and biomorphic forms that under
 line their pursuit of simple forms inspired by nature.\n\nAssorted Flavors
 : Pence Member Exhibit | Mar. 13 - Apr. 16\n\nOur 2nd annual non-juried ex
 hibit celebrates the creativity and talent of our organization’s support
 ers\, showcasing work in different media by 40 Pence Members.\n\nBarbara P
 rodaniuk: Myths in Mud | Mar. 13 - Apr. 26\n\nThe ceramic artist’s work 
 is inspired by the forest\, meadows\, and waterways surrounding the Trucke
 e area. She explores the stories carried by the creatures and artifacts fo
 und in these environments through layered surfaces\, organic textures\, an
 d sculpted imagery.\n\nJulie Bernadeth Crumb: Stairway Show | Apr. 4 - May
  17\n\nView the artist’s collection of work featured along the stairway.
 \n\nScavenger Hunt: Join us for a fun\, art-themed scavenger hunt at the P
 ence during the 2nd Friday ArtAbout. Complete all of the clues by explorin
 g our exhibits for the chance to win a special prize.\n\n—\n\nVisit the 
 Pence and other venues in Downtown Davis for the 2nd Friday ArtAbout artwa
 lk. We will have printed ArtAbout guides available that week. Follow the A
 rtAbout’s Facebook page for more information: https://www.facebook.com/d
 avisartabout.
LOCATION:212 D Street\, Davis\, CA 95616
URL:https://web.davischamber.com/events/2nd%20Friday%20ArtAbout%20at%20the
 %20Pence%20Gallery-5712/details
X-SOURCE:Davis Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
